<p><span>来源：<span>中新网</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-09-22 08:59</p>
<p><i><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200922/f887cf6afd3c460daaf68ac5cae5adc1.jpeg" /></i></p>
<p><i><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200922/d180c9bc9b47402ca71efc9600246433.jpeg" /></i></p>
